    "passage": "I like my home. I can go to school and I can go to the park. My school is here. The park is there. I go to the store with my mom. We see a big store and a small store. I like the zoo too. I can see a lot of animals at the zoo. My dad is at the hospital, but he is OK. I like school, park, store, and zoo very much!",
